                <head>[Per Atlantic cable.]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1866-09-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">September</hi> 19, 1866</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Plate affair settled. Washburn notified to pass blockade.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>JAMES WATSON WEBB.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward,</hi>
                        <hi rend="italic">Secretary of State, Washington, D. C.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
